## install nerd font

```sh
brew tap homebrew/cask-fonts
brew install --cask font-nerd-fonts
```

## install powerline fonts (legacy)

```sh
# clone
git clone https://github.com/powerline/fonts.git --depth=1
# install
cd fonts
./install.sh
```


## install starship - terminal UI

```sh
brew install starship
```

## install mise - version manager

```sh
brew install mise
```

## android adb via wifi

```sh
adb tcpip 5555 from a command prompt
adb shell "ip addr show wlan0 | grep -e wlan0$ | cut -d\" \" -f 6 | cut -d/ -f 1" 
# to obtain the phone's IP address Disconnect USB cable and run adb connect <ip_address>:5555
```

## git submodule

```sh
git submodule update
```